---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/react/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/react/Footer.jsx';
import ContactForm from '../components/react/ContactForm.jsx';
import { Mail, Phone, MapPin, Clock } from 'lucide-react';
---

<Layout title="Contacto - Impulso Tecnológico">
  <Navbar client:load />
  
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative pt-16 pb-5 lg:pt-24 lg:pb-8 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-cyan-50/30 to-blue-50/40">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 px-4 py-2 bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
            <span>Contacto</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
            Hablemos de tu 
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-600 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
              Proyecto Digital
            </span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Estamos listos para ayudarte a transformar tu empresa. Completa el formulario y nos pondremos en contacto contigo lo antes posible.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
          <!-- Contact Form -->
          <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
                Envíanos un mensaje
              </h2>
              <ContactForm client:load />
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact Info -->
          <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Información de contacto
              </h2>
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
                Nuestro equipo está disponible para responder tus consultas y ayudarte a encontrar la mejor solución para tu negocio.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Contact Cards -->
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <!-- Email -->
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-cyan-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                  <Mail className="w-6 h-6" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Email</h3>
                  <a href="mailto:contacto@impulsotecnologico.cl" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-cyan-600 transition-colors">
                    contacto@impulsotecnologico.cl
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phone -->
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-cyan-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                  <Phone className="w-6 h-6" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Teléfono</h3>
                  <a href="tel:+56912345678" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-cyan-600 transition-colors">
                    +56 9 8901 9541
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Location -->
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-cyan-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                  <MapPin className="w-6 h-6" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Ubicación</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-600">
                    Rancagua, Chile
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Hours -->
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-cyan-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 group">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                  <Clock className="w-6 h-6" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Horario</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-600">
                    Lunes a Viernes<br />
                    9:00 - 18:00
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Additional Info -->
            <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-blue-50 rounded-xl border border-cyan-200">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                ¿Prefieres una reunión virtual?
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4">
                Agenda una videollamada con nuestro equipo para discutir tu proyecto en detalle.
              </p>
              <a 
                href="#"
                class="inline-flex items-center text-cyan-600 hover:text-blue-600 font-medium transition-colors"
              >
                Agendar reunión →
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
            Preguntas Frecuentes
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Respuestas a las consultas más comunes
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">
              <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">¿Cuál es el tiempo de respuesta?</span>
              <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600">
              Respondemos todas las consultas en un plazo máximo de 24 horas hábiles.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">
              <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">¿Ofrecen consultas gratuitas?</span>
              <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600">
              Sí, la primera consulta es completamente gratuita. Es una oportunidad para conocer tu proyecto y proponer soluciones.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">
              <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">¿Trabajan con empresas fuera de Chile?</span>
              <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600">
              Sí, trabajamos con clientes en toda Latinoamérica de forma remota.
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer client:load />
</Layout>